description:
2009 TAG TEAM LEAGUE IN FRONT OF A LIVE AUDIENCE
TEAM ICE
Hollie & Bella
Combined HT:132'
Combined WT: 305lbs
Season Record:(0-3)
THE GODDESSES
Ami & Adrianna
Combined HT:134"
Combined WT: 278lbs
Season Record:(0-3)
Welcome to Ultimate Surrender's 2009 Tag Team League.
Team Ice vs The Goddesses. Three girls,
non-scripted, real tag team action.
This is the 2009 Tag Team Season. New teams; new wrestlers. The Beginning of what will be the most brutal Tag Team Season yet!
It all comes down to this one match for both of these teams. If the Goddesses win, they will go to the playoffs and face The Dragons. If Team Ice wins there will be a 3 way tie for 3rd place, and they will win the tie breaker (highest points for the season) and they will make the playoffs.
The whole season all riding on one match up! Winner moves forward, loser goes home with nothing.
title: LIVE TAG TEAM LEAGUE
